<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Welcome to UniSync</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #F5EDD8; padding: 24px 16px; }
  .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1408 0%, #2C1E08 60%, #1A1408 100%);
    border-radius: 18px 18px 0 0;
    padding: 36px 36px 30px;
    text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .header-accent {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #CDA96A, #BC6F37, #CDA96A, transparent);
  }
  .welcome-emoji { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }
  .header h1 { font-size: 1.55rem; font-weight: 700; color: #F5EAD2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .header p { font-size: 0.90rem; color: rgba(245,234,210,0.65); }
  .body { background: #FFFBEF; padding: 32px 36px; }
  .greeting { font-size: 1.10rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1608; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .text { font-size: 0.90rem; color: #5A4418; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .feature-list { margin: 20px 0; }
  .feature-item {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(188,111,55,0.10);
  }
  .feature-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .feature-icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 10px; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: rgba(188,111,55,0.10); border: 1px solid rgba(188,111,55,0.20);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .feature-info .title { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1C1608; }
  .feature-info .desc  { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #9A7D4A; margin-top: 2px; }
  .cta-wrap { text-align: center; padding: 26px 0 8px; }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #BC6F37, #9A5A2C);
    color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none;
    padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(188,111,55,0.40);
  }
  .footer {
    background: #1A1408; border-radius: 0 0 18px 18px;
    padding: 18px 36px; text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(205,169,106,0.55); line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .footer strong { color: #CDA96A; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-accent"></div>
    <span class="welcome-emoji">🎓</span>
    <h1>Welcome to UniSync!</h1>
    <p>Rabindra University, Bangladesh · Dept. of Management</p>
  </div>

  <div class="body">
    <div class="greeting">Hi {{ user_name }}, you're all set! 🎉</div>
    <p class="text">
      Your UniSync account is ready. Please verify your email by clicking the link sent by Supabase, then sign in to access your personal academic portal.
    </p>

    <div class="feature-list">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">📅</div>
        <div class="feature-info">
          <div class="title">Class Routine</div>
          <div class="desc">Your semester's live schedule with real-time class tracking</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
        <div class="feature-info">
          <div class="title">Task Manager</div>
          <div class="desc">Track assignments, deadlines and study goals</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">📧</div>
        <div class="feature-info">
          <div class="title">Daily Email Summary</div>
          <div class="desc">Every evening at 7 PM — tomorrow's classes + pending tasks sent to this email</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">📁</div>
        <div class="feature-info">
          <div class="title">Study Resources</div>
          <div class="desc">Upload and share notes, files and study materials</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-wrap">
      <a href="https://unisync.example.com/auth/login" class="cta-btn">
        Sign In Now →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <strong>UniSync</strong> · Rabindra University, Bangladesh<br>
    Department of Management · Academic Portal<br>
    <span style="font-size:0.65rem;">You registered with this email. If this wasn't you, please ignore.</span>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>